	(text_box "Board Description:\n\nThis board seeks to integrate logic controller board that additionally includes temperature, humidity, voltage, and current sensors and manages the RC control logic for the drive train. Additionally, I would like this board to handle Arm control forwarding from the Nvidia Jetson from the network switch.\n\nThis board will utilize an on board processor to handle Rover telemetry, relay arm control commands from the Nvidia Jetson to the arm, and Host a Web server for remote control via our comms RF interface. This board will also handle power sequencing for subsystem control, allowing it to control whether the Arm subsystem is being powered, and whether the Drivetrain system is being powered, that way we can regulate this ourselves over a remote connection."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 15.875 19.685 0)
		(size 125.73 22.86)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
		(stroke
			(width 0)
			(type solid)
		)
		(fill
			(type none)
		)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
				(thickness 0.254)
				(bold yes)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
		(uuid "1e4b295e-ae73-48ec-b48b-9c4b1a796f9a")
	)
